OL,3,CThird of employers 'likely to make
OL,4,Cstaff redundancies by start of 2027'
OL,6,FOne in three employers are likely to
OL,7,Fmake staff redundancies by the start
OL,8,Fof next year, new research suggests.
OL,10,FA survey of 1,000 businesses by the
OL,11,Fconciliation service Acas found that
OL,12,Flarger ones are more likely to lay off
OL,13,Fstaff than smaller firms.
OL,15,FAcas director of dispute resolution
OL,16,FKevin Rowan said: "The results of our
OL,17,Fpoll reveal that a third of businesses
OL,18,Fare considering redundancies by the
OL,19,Fstart of next year.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
