OL,3,CThird of employers 'likely to make
OL,4,Cstaff redundancies by start of 2027'
OL,6,F"Organisations should look at all
OL,7,Fpossible alternatives to redundancies
OL,8,Ffirst, but if employers conclude they
OL,9,Fhave no choice, then they have legal
OL,10,Frequirements they must follow.
OL,12,F"This means they must consult with
OL,13,Fstaff early to seek their views, or
OL,14,Frisk being subject to a costly legal
OL,15,Fprocess."
